page.title: 11PARKES PORSCHE,EXETER.
page.content: Parks Porsche is situated next to Weddels slaughter house in St.Thomas. Parks was formed in 1980 because the director lived there.They believed there was a gap in the market and nobody was selling Porshes in the South West.The nearest place that sells Porsches is in Bournemouth. Porsche cars are highly sophis- ticated for maximum performance.Their owners range from being rich business men to ordinary working men.Porsches can reach high speeds ranging from 160 mph to 127 mph. Porsches are expensive cars but their owners believe them to be worth-while.Their costs range from Â£13500 to Â£35000.Porsche have a lot of extras such as compact stereo,electric windows,heated wing mirror and aerial. There are truly luxury cars.No wonder Parks are proud of these German cars.
